data.description: There is so much room to roam at this beautiful northwest home. It features four large bedrooms, two living areas and an amazing master bath. The interior has all new paint, flooring, blinds and appliances. The lot is huge with plenty of room for RV parking. The backyard features two patios and a large tuff shed. Roof and A/C have been updated. The entire septic system is brand new. Solar is a power purchase agreement with Vivint. Please click the virtual media link above right to see a video and a 360 tour.
